title: About Me
text: I’m a Junior at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln, majoring in Sports Media and Communications with a minor in Entrepreneurship. I specialize in portrait and sports photography, capturing the energy and emotion of every moment. Alongside my visual work, I enjoy combining storytelling with analytics to dive into the numbers behind the games. I’m passionate about blending creativity with strategy, allowing me to craft impactful stories both through imagery and data. Always seeking new opportunities to grow, I aim to push the boundaries of my work, whether through collaborations or personal projects.
